<div class='pages-carousel__content inverse module'>
<a class='pages-carousel__heading' href='/read/ted-books/ted-books-library/how-we-ll-live-on-mars'>How We'll Live on Mars</a>
<div class='pages-carousel__text'>
<div class='pages-carousel__body'>
<p>In this sweeping, provocative book, award-winning journalist Stephen Petranek makes the case that living on Mars is an essential backup plan for humanity and explains in fascinating detail just how it will happen.</p>

</div>
</div>
<div class='pages-carousel__credit'>Stephen Petranek </div>
<a class='pages-carousel__link button button--dark' href='/read/ted-books/ted-books-library/how-we-ll-live-on-mars'>Learn more</a>
