<div class='pages-carousel__content inverse module'>
<a class='pages-carousel__heading' href='/read/ted-books/ted-books-library/judge-this'>Judge This</a>
<div class='pages-carousel__text'>
<div class='pages-carousel__body'>
<p>Designer Chip Kidd reveals the hidden secrets behind design choices, and, along the way, shows how so much of our world can be a dazzling magic show, a seductive work of art, and a sublime experience â if we have the tools to judge it.</p>

</div>
</div>
<div class='pages-carousel__credit'>Chip Kidd</div>
<a class='pages-carousel__link button button--dark' href='/read/ted-books/ted-books-library/judge-this'>Learn more</a>
