<div class='pages-carousel__content inverse module'>
<a class='pages-carousel__heading' href='/read/ted-books/ted-books-library/follow-your-gut'>Follow Your Gut</a>
<div class='pages-carousel__text'>
<div class='pages-carousel__body'>
<p>Dr. Rob Knight reveals the groundbreaking science behind the microscopic life within our bodies, and the astonishing impact microbes have on our health, mood, and more. </p>

</div>
</div>
<div class='pages-carousel__credit'>Rob Knight with Brendan Buhler</div>
<a class='pages-carousel__link button button--dark' href='/read/ted-books/ted-books-library/follow-your-gut'>Learn more</a>
