<div class='pages-carousel__content inverse module'>
<a class='pages-carousel__heading' href='/read/ted-books/ted-books-library/the-future-of-architecture'>The Future of Architecture in 100 Buildings</a>
<div class='pages-carousel__text'>
<div class='pages-carousel__body'>
<p>With stunning photography and stories of architectural wonder from across the globe, this book illustrates the rapidly evolving world of architecture in the digital age.</p>

</div>
</div>
<div class='pages-carousel__credit'>Marc Kushner </div>
<a class='pages-carousel__link button button--dark' href='/read/ted-books/ted-books-library/the-future-of-architecture'>Learn more</a>
