<div class='pages-carousel__text'>
<div class='pages-carousel__body'>
<p>In <em>The Mathematics of Love</em>, Dr. Hannah Fry takes the reader on a fascinating journey through the patterns that define our love lives, tackling some of the most common yet complex questions surrounding love.</p>

</div>
</div>
<div class='pages-carousel__credit'>Hannah Fry</div>
