<h3 class="h4 m4">TED Books box sets</h3>

<p>TED Books are now available in three specially curated collections: <a href="/read/ted-books/ted-books-library/box-sets#h2--ted-books-box-set-the-completist"><em>The Completist</em></a>, <a href="/read/ted-books/ted-books-library/box-sets#h2--ted-books-box-set-the-science-mind"><em>The Science Mind</em></a>, and <a href="/read/ted-books/ted-books-library/box-sets#h2--ted-books-box-set-the-creative-mind"><em>The Creative Mind</em></a>. These beautiful box sets are designed to let readers dive deeply into their favorite topics. </p>

<p><a href="/read/ted-books/ted-books-library/box-sets">Explore the TED Books box sets</a> </p>

